AZd17w</a><br />\nSpotify <a href=\"http://spoti.fi/2AnLA84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fspoti.fi%2F2AnLA84&d=l4n5bHCFn6JX4ua1sAVs%2FF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=0aacb47e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://spoti.fi/2AnLA84</a><br />\nMusic One <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2jrsRhg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2jrsRhg&d=l4n5bHCFn6JX4ua1sAVs%2FF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=011a8b81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2jrsRhg</a>"},{"pid":"065a4d5fe129b2ab71b648441d2837b5fd43251a","tid":493604,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:10:59.000Z","msg":"簡介：用了最大的力氣工作，偷閑時何不也來個盡力，給自己勇氣抽離一下，吸收天地靈氣，充電後，向前的步伐更扎實！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n懸浮在天空 漫遊極光中 七彩光映照牽引我入夢<br />\n或潛入水中 和鯨魚相擁 呼吸於水裏轉眼已學懂<br />\n<br />\n雙手鬆開了 化做了清風 皺過了眉再放鬆 再露笑容<br />\n<br />\n完全未怕冷 寒冰之山綻放的花 紅泛著兩眼 淚水總可力抗風沙<br />\n只需要 帶著那傷疤 看看不朽的美麗晚霞 苦水都蒸發<br />\n<br />\n未來像幅畫 但無力揮灑 當身邊只有操縱與漫罵<br />\n甜言在嘴巴 難明瞭真假 都不想深究想再次玩耍<br />\n<br />\n不必多牽掛 偶然有雨灑 雨季過後那煙花 格外更璀燦<br />\n<br />\n遊歷大世界 能一登天際那梯階 尋覓在某處 能千秋不變老的街<br />\n只需要 放下那煲呔 確信給我灑脱換對鞋 一身都輕快<br />\n<br />\n討厭、妒忌、善忘、悶氣 通通想叫我倒地 未曾折服自信可再飛起<br />\n<br />\n遊歷大世界 能一登天際那梯階 尋覓在某處 能千秋不變老的街<br />\n不知道 結局懶去猜 哪怕給我天氣漸變壊<br />\n<br />\n塵落在世界 浮生一刻踏破鐘擺 心都開過了 至少都不會再拖拉<br />\n不知道 結局懶去猜 哪怕給我天氣漸變壊 瀟灑的姿態"},{"pid":"724c79aa8d0f49146a63b14e973a06bcf70e512a","tid":493604,"uid":4260,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:14:46.000Z","msg":"今年另外三首派台作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n王菀之 Ivana Wong - 突然一生人 (Official MV) <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wRJXEsBrkW8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwRJXEsBrkW8&d=l4n5bHCFn6JX4ua1sAVs%2FF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=4afbfff5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wRJXEsBrkW8</a><br />\n曲：王菀之 詞：林夕<br />\n編曲/監製：馮翰銘<br />\n<br />\n王菀之 Ivana Wong - 愛不曾遺忘任何人 (Official MV) <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lO4-g9RwaRM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlO4-g9RwaRM&d=l4n5bHCFn6JX4ua1sAVs%2FF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9aa7b95f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lO4-g9RwaRM</a><br />\n曲：王菀之 詞：小克<br />\n編/監 : 馮翰銘<br />\n<br />\n王菀之 Ivana Wong - 忘記有時 (Official MV) <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JpZxhuklvmk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJpZxhuklvmk&d=l4n5bHCFn6JX4ua1sAVs%2FF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=ae9f9e43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JpZxhuklvmk</a><br />\n曲：王菀之詞：林夕<br />\n編：馮翰銘 監：馮翰銘"},{"pid":"d36ae6e58b0c1e5c86a476161065498a80e6ab12","tid":493604,"uid":55800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:28:24.000Z","msg":"個旋律好特別，聽前半段果陣完全無expect後半段會係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4e23c8c49ad16db921ed93017c4f90b96f48cb","tid":493604,"uid":4260,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:58:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個旋律好特別，聽前半段果陣完全無expect後半段會係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好鍾意段bridge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好有描離現實既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推介聽埋佢有首舊歌叫最好的，我覺得編曲去得盡好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y98x6TkSX9c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY98x6TkSX9c&d=l4n5bHCFn6JX4ua1sAVs%2FF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=cb14a007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://